collections.name: Krystyna Milewski - My Secret Garden
collections.description:
My work is a dialogue between inner and outer landscapes. A reflection of both the natural world and the emotions it stirs within us. Through painting, I explore the rhythm of nature, capturing its vibrancy, movement and poetry. Flowers, foliage, and organic forms become a language of color and texture, allowing me to express a deep connection to the world around me. My work is an invitation to find joy in the beauty of both nature and the emotions it awakens.

I have always found solace in tending to my garden, watching it flourish with care and time. After a profound change in my life and the loss of my cherished space, I turned to painting to recreate it. My Secret Garden I is a personal exploration of memory, nature, and renewal—transforming my connection to the natural world into a vibrant sanctuary on canvas.

All photos were professionally taken and digitized by Alice Milewski.

collections.name: TranosPhotography
collections.description:
Manos Dimitranopoulos
Street & Portrait Photographer | Visual Storyteller

I am a passionate photographer specializing in street photography and portraiture. Through my lens, I aim to capture raw emotions, fleeting moments, and the essence of human connection. My work explores the intersection of light, shadow, and composition to create compelling visual narratives.

With a keen eye for detail and a deep appreciation for storytelling, I strive to turn everyday scenes into powerful images that evoke emotion and curiosity. Whether it’s a candid street shot or an intimate portrait, my goal is to present authentic perspectives that resonate with the viewer.

Now bringing my work to the digital space, I am excited to share my photography through NFTs, offering collectors unique, one-of-a-kind moments frozen in time.

Let’s connect and explore the art of visual storytelling together.

collections.name: Singularis
collections.description:
Singularis presents standalone pieces that capture the real sky during sacred, historical, or deeply symbolic moments 🌟🔐🤯

 Each work is based on an unrepeatable event, traced with astronomical precision and transformed into art through programming, science, and spiritual sensitivity. The stars shown were visible at that exact moment above Earth, using verified coordinates and data from the Hipparcos catalog (ESA–NASA).

 Every piece includes a scientific guide and a Starfield Certificate, validating the authenticity of each celestial coordinate.

🔭 One sky. One moment. One truth.
